text: Captain Cassian Andor is a character from Star Wars who is in the movie Rogue One. He is played by actor Diego Luna. Cassian Andor was a soldier for the Rebel Alliance and helped the Rebel Alliance steal the plans to the Death Star. During the battle, Andor was killed with the rest of his team but the mission was a success. Cassian Andor will appear in his own show, Andor released in 2022. ==References== Category:Star Wars characters Category:Fictional characters introduced in 2016
